{"tid":1677803,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【重要】 對於 11.3 另一個維園集會有疑問？張文宣是唔是玩搞笑？","createTime":"2019-10-27T10:07:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-28T01:13:33.000Z","uid":167548,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a61ddf698487bc20dfc88cbc0d7f9d2eda78c04f","tid":1677803,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T10:07:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HLLzKde.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHLLzKde.jpg&h=d6530769&s={SIZE}\" />  <br />\n<br />\n11.3 點解唔申請不反？<br />\n就因為主題是反公安條例？<br />\n入去維園申請被捕？<br />\n維園是<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">好難離開</span></strong>, 比起梳士巴利公園。<br />\n同埋成個模式同埋11.2攬炒集會一鳩樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個情況會好似10.27一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然攬炒集會都未必有不反<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但是沒不反去維園坐是想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你出去SOGO都易走啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JmDmpgg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJmDmpgg.jpg&h=33afb475&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢兩個星期六，大家記得去，兩個主題都好juicy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n11.2 記得印張維吾爾旗<br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nOdJCDp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnOdJCDp.png&h=b0884bd5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n睇返文宣組11.3號集會好似取消左？ </span></span></strong><br />\n同埋11.2加11.3分散左人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n攬炒都寫左<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">暫定</span></strong>維園<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你沒不反, 入去維園得淡笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你是有權去遊行集會, 但是不被捕是更重要！<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">有沒人可以搞定plan B如果沒不反, 去邊度集合？繼續港島？</span></strong>"},{"pid":"9611780204d023d8809181035764da3c62b80ef7","tid":1677803,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T10:07:41.000Z","msg":"【黃色經濟】有個傻仔整咗個黃藍商鋪認證平台<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eqgeNS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eqgeNS</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2dbabba0a0e55f2212a52d4ed2959bc990b407c","tid":1677803,"uid":213747,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T10:09:01.000Z","msg":"11月3第一次聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c76b0004301af1733f66e0a979a66d611da7d123","tid":1677803,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T10:09:18.000Z","msg":"比錯負評 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2c1de4089607b508be9f2112253751e7ada2f07","tid":1677803,"uid":63639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T10:11:00.000Z","msg":"照申請 唔批另一件事 照可以聚到人"},{"pid":"ab262d5ed5800c5f03156a59c7474e34d1c253b8","tid":1677803,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2dbabba0a0e55f2212a52d4ed2959bc990b407c","tid":1677803,"uid":213747,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T10:09:01.000Z","msg":"11月3第一次聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T10:12:15.000Z","msg":"真是on9架張文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我聽返個version是11.3集會搞先, <br />\n但是呢攬炒同埋劉生想112(國際救助電話)<br />\n做gimmick所以推左11.2維園集會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但是呢樣文宣由初頭講合併, 再到呢家見返佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想confirm是唔是照搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申去11.2, 唔去11.3<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"530a14bac70a302b58b0ef965b98910ffaf71667","tid":1677803,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c76b0004301af1733f66e0a979a66d611da7d123","tid":1677803,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T10:09:18.000Z","msg":"比錯負評 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T10:12:41.000Z","msg":"喂 屌比正評啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b394033eb60f577292e69eb69836caf5870460e1","tid":1677803,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f2c1de4089607b508be9f2112253751e7ada2f07","tid":1677803,"uid":63639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T10:11:00.000Z","msg":"照申請 唔批另一件事 照可以聚到人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T10:13:55.000Z","msg":"但是11.3沒申請<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&nbsp;<br />\n同埋我講緊<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">攬炒11.2</span></strong>同埋<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">非攬炒11.3</span></strong>兩個重覆集會<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3da5eec742e0ab9d0ee9f94f57ed0c09b2757688","tid":1677803,"uid":145884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T10:14:46.000Z","msg":"[警世]狗狗轉左玩法<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1677812\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1677812</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"87f8713f4450f7e85e51a02c503819ff848eef81","tid":1677803,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T10:16:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fffb59b4bb31c37fc304319fc9e8695cedb6c1e7","ti